  "title": "Security",
  "description": "<p><strong>Security Officer (Industrial Building)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ol><li>Responsible for daily security operations of the industrial\n     building, including access control for personnel and vehicles;</li><li>Conduct regular patrols of common areas such as factory zones,\n     car parks, elevators, and corridors;</li><li>Manage visitors, contractors, renovation and maintenance\n     personnel, including verification of passes and documents;</li><li>Maintain on-site order and respond to incidents or emergencies\n     when required;</li><li>Support property management in implementing security policies,\n     fire safety procedures, and emergency drills;</li><li>Maintain daily security logs and incident records.</li></ol><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ol><li>Physically fit, responsible, and able to work on shift\n     schedules;</li><li>Prior experience in industrial parks, commercial buildings, or\n     property security is preferred;</li><li>Basic communication skills; English communication ability is an\n     advantage;</li><li>Familiar with basic security and fire safety procedures;</li><li>Disciplined, reliable, and able to follow instructions.</li></ol>",
